<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px; background: #f5f5f5; color: #333; } .email-container {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; } .header {
      text-align: center; background: #e74c3c; color: #fff; padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; } .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; }
      .content p { font-size: 14px; } .details { font-size: 14px; margin: 15px
      0; } .details div { margin-bottom: 8px; } .footer { text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
        <p>Unfortunately, your payment for the appointment could not be
          processed.</p>

        <div class="details">
          <div><strong>Attempted Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</div>
          <div><strong>Amount:</strong> {{totalAmount}} {{currency}}</div>
          <div><strong>Specialist:</strong> {{specialistName}}</div>
          <div><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}, {{branch}}</div>
        </div>

        <p>Please try again using a valid payment method. If you need help,
          contact our support team.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        You're receiving this email because you booked an appointment with
        Meldy.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>